ride'=>'Typeoverstyring','Room override'=>'Romoversyring','Existing booking'=>'Eksisterende bestilling','Blocked/Closed'=>'Blokkert/Stengt','Weekend pricing'=>'Helgepriser','Holiday pricing'=>'Helligdagspriser','Pro license required to download invoices.'=>'Pro-lisens kreves for å laste ned fakturaer.','Booking not found.'=>'Bestillingen ble ikke funnet.','Invoice for Booking #%d'=>'Faktura for bestilling #%d','Configure Company Profile'=>'Konfigurer firmaprofil','—'=>'—','Guest Details'=>'Gjestetaljer','Ref'=>'Ref','Required / Not Received'=>'Påkrevd / Ikke mottatt','Actual Payment Amount'=>'Faktisk betalt beløp','INVOICE'=>'FAKTURA','Chat with %s AI Concierge'=>'Chat med %s AI-concierge','Real-time AI chat assistant for room availability, policies, and booking support.'=>'Chat-assistent for tilgjengelighet, vilkår og bookingstøtte i sanntid.','AI Concierge Chat'=>'AI-concierge-chat','JavaScript is required for the AI Concierge. You can also %s.'=>'JavaScript kreves for AI Concierge. Du kan også %s.','book directly here'=>'bestill direkte her','block descriptionEmbed the AI Concierge chat widget anywhere on your site.'=>'Bygg inn AI Concierge-widgeten hvor som helst på nettstedet ditt.','block keywordai'=>'ai','block keywordconcierge'=>'concierge','AI Resilience Engine reset. All failure scores and cooldowns cleared.'=>'AI Resilience Engine tilbakestilt.','Operational'=>'Operativ','Cooling Down (Demand Spike)'=>'Kjøler ned (topp i etterspørsel)','High Demand (Degraded)'=>'Høy etterspørsel (redusert)','Service Health'=>'Tjenestehelse','Resuming in %1$d seconds...'=>'Gjenopptar om %1$d sekunder...','Error Score'=>'Feilscore','Manually clear the demand cooldown and reset failure scores.'=>'Fjern nedkøling og nullstill feilscorer manuelt.','Notice: Cost Resilience'=>'Merknad: Kostnadsresiliens','To ensure your guests always receive a response, the system may automatically fallback to secondary models if your chosen model is unavailable. This may result in higher than expected billable token costs.'=>'For å sikre at gjestene alltid får svar, kan systemet automatisk bruke reservemodeller. Dette kan medføre høyere kostnader.','OpenAI (GPT-5.4)'=>'OpenAI (GPT-5.4)','Anthropic (Claude 4.6)'=>'Anthropic (Claude 4.6)','Gemini 3.1 Flash-Lite Preview ⚡ Recommended'=>'Gemini 3.1 Flash-Lite Preview ⚡ Anbefalt','Gemini 3.1 Flash Preview (Balanced)'=>'Gemini 3.1 Flash Preview (Balansert)','Gemini 3.1 Pro Preview (Flagship)'=>'Gemini 3.1 Pro Preview (Flaggskip)','Gemini 2.5 Flash — Stable'=>'Gemini 2.5 Flash — Stabil','Gemini 2.5 Flash-Lite — Stable (Lightest)'=>'Gemini 2.5 Flash-Lite — Stabil (Lettest)','Gemini 2.5 Pro — Stable (Highest Quality)'=>'Gemini 2.5 Pro — Stabil (Høyeste kvalitet)','GPT-5.4 Mini ⚡ (Fast & Smart)'=>'GPT-5.4 Mini ⚡ (Rask og smart)','GPT-5.4 Frontier (Flagship Intelligence)'=>'GPT-5.4 Frontier (Flaggskip-intelligens)','GPT-4o (Legacy Stable)'=>'GPT-4o (Gammel stabil)','GPT-4o Mini (Legacy Budget)'=>'GPT-4o Mini (Gammel budsjett)','Claude Sonnet 4.6 (Most Balanced)'=>'Claude Sonnet 4.6 (Best balansert)','Claude Opus 4.6 (Supreme Reasoning)'=>'Claude Opus 4.6 (Høyeste resonnering)','Claude 3.5 Sonnet (Legacy)'=>'Claude 3.5 Sonnet (Gammel)','Reasoning Intensity'=>'Resonneringsintensitet','Auto (Balanced)'=>'Auto (Balansert)','Low (Speed Focused)'=>'Lav (Hastighetsfokus)','Medium (Deeper Reasoning)'=>'Middels (Dypere resonnering)','High (Advanced Complex)'=>'Høy (Avansert/Kompleks)','Higher intensity increases intelligence and accuracy but raises operational token costs. (GPT-5.4 & Claude 4.6+)'=>'Høyere intensitet øker intelligensen, men også kostnadene. (GPT-5.4 & Claude 4.6+)','Fallback models are used when the primary connection is overloaded. Note: Fallback models may have different pricing profiles than your primary selection.'=>'Reservemodeller brukes ved overbelastning. Merk: Prisene kan variere.','The chat sessions table could not be created. Please deactivate and reactivate the plugin, or contact support.'=>'T